## 🌐 Paso 6: Configurar Reverse Proxy (Opcional pero Recomendado)

### 6.1 Nginx Configuration

**Para Provider** (`/etc/nginx/sites-available/auth.acceleralia.com`):

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name auth.acceleralia.com;

    # Redirigir HTTP a HTTPS
    return 301 https://$server_name$request_uri;
}

server {
    listen 443 ssl http2;
    server_name auth.acceleralia.com;

    ssl_certificate /path/to/cert.pem;
    ssl_certificate_key /path/to/key.pem;

    location / {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:8080;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection 'upgrade';
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
        proxy_cache_bypass $http_upgrade;
    }
}
```

**Para Backend** (`/etc/nginx/sites-available/api.acceleralia.com`):

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name api.acceleralia.com;
    return 301 https://$server_name$request_uri;
}

server {
    listen 443 ssl http2;
    server_name api.acceleralia.com;

    ssl_certificate /path/to/cert.pem;
    ssl_certificate_key /path/to/key.pem;

    location / {
        proxy_pass http://localhost:8080;
        proxy_http_version 1.1;
        proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
        proxy_set_header Connection 'upgrade';
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
        proxy_cache_bypass $http_upgrade;
    }
}
```

**Para Frontend** (`/etc/nginx/sites-available/app.acceleralia.com`):

```nginx
server {
    listen 80;
    server_name app.acceleralia.com;
    return 301 https://$server_name$request_uri;
}

server {
    listen 443 ssl http2;
    server_name app.acceleralia.com;

    ssl_certificate /path/to/cert.pem;
    ssl_certificate_key /path/to/key.pem;

    root /ruta/completa/a/oidc-server/frontend/src;
    index index.html;

    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ /index.html;
    }
}
```

### 6.2 Habilitar Sitios

```bash
# Crear enlaces simbólicos
sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/auth.acceleralia.com /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/
sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/api.acceleralia.com /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/
sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/app.acceleralia.com /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/

# Verificar configuración
sudo nginx -t

# Recargar nginx
sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

**IMPORTANTE**: Si usas nginx, debes configurar `TRUST_PROXY=1` en `backend/.env`

